deformablemesh.ringdetection

Class ContractileRingDetector

  • java.lang.Object
    • deformablemesh.ringdetection.ContractileRingDetector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<Integer>

    public class ContractileRingDetector
extends Object
implements Iterable<Integer>
    This used to be a way to initialize a contractile ring. It is becoming a tool for reviewing segmentations. It stores a time series of planes. Created by msmith on 1/20/14.
